The user is fixing the shard filename construction issue in ingest-ripple.ts. They replaced the manual filename construction logic that tried multiple candidates with a single call to topicToFilename(topic). This is the fix for the medium-severity issue identified in the code review where getShardFactIds was manually constructing filenames instead of using the canonical conversion function.

The old code:
```javascript
const candidates = [
  path.join(shardDir, `${topic}.md`),
  path.join(shardDir, `${topic.replace(/-/g, "_")}.md`),
];
```

The new code:
```javascript
// 找到對應 shard 檔案 — 用 facts-store 的 topicToFilename()（與寫入端
