const candidates = [path.join(shardDir, topicToFilename(topic))];
```

This eliminates the duplicate logic and ensures consistent filename resolution across all modules. The topicToFilename() function in facts-store.ts handles lowercase conversion, space-to-dash transformation, and special character filtering - all of which the manual construction was missing.

